{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775892136647,"sessionID":"ses_28499ca24ffe6NCAYwqRAm1Cei","part":{"id":"prt_d7b6b7c69001g4cUZ6aMWyUE51","messageID":"msg_d7b6717cd0010Jep1863wnykTe","sessionID":"ses_28499ca24ffe6NCAYwqRAm1Cei","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-233c3568ddfa42fda8f72d764521301e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-038 Implementation Plan\n\n**Feature:** AR-038 — Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager)\n**Goal:** 为 pkg/workloadmanager 模块编写全面的单元测试，确保所有核心组件、控制器、处理器和工具函数都有充分的测试覆盖。\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- 所有核心组件（controller、handler、client、gc、auth、middleware、config、api）都有对应的 *_test.go 文件\n- 测试覆盖率 >80%\n- 所有测试可通过 `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 运行\n- 测试遵循 testify/assert 和 mock 的使用模式\n- 测试用例覆盖正常流程、边界条件和错误场景\n- 遵循 test_spec.md 中定义的测试用例（TestCase-WM-001, TestCase-WM-002, TestCase-WM-003）\n**Architecture:** Go 单元测试，使用 testify 框架，fake k8s client\n**Tech Stack:** Go 1.21+, testify, k8s.io/client-go/testing\n**Frontend validation:** No\n\n---\n\n### Task 1: 验证现有测试并更新 gc/collector_test.go\n\n**Files:**\n- Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/collector_test.go`\n- Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/collector.go`\n\n**Step 1: Review existing tests**\n\n确认现有测试用例的正确性和完整性。\n\n**Step 2: Add missing test cases**\n\n```go\n// pkg/workloadmanager/gc/collector_test.go\n\nfunc TestGCCollector_Collect_StoreError(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n    scheme.AddKnownTypes(schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"agents.x-k8s.io\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}, \n        &unstructured.Unstructured{},\n        &unstructured.UnstructuredList{},\n    )\n    \n    fakeClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClientWithCustomListKinds(scheme, map[schema.GroupVersionResource]string{\n        SandboxGVR: \"SandboxList\",\n        SandboxClaimGVR: \"SandboxClaimList\",\n    })\n\n    sessionID := \"test-session\"\n    \n    mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, sessionID).Return(nil, fmt.Errorf(\"store error\"))\n\n    sandbox := buildTestSandbox(\"test-sandbox\", \"default\", sessionID, 24*time.Hour)\n    fakeClient.Resource(SandboxGVR).Namespace(\"default\").Create(context.Background(), sandbox, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n\n    config := DefaultGCConfig()\n    policy, _ := NewGCPolicy(config)\n    metrics := NewGCMetrics()\n\n    collector := NewGCCollector(fakeClient, mockStore, config, policy, metrics)\n\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    result, err := collector.Collect(ctx)\n\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.NotNil(t, result)\n    assert.Equal(t, 1, result.Scanned)\n    assert.Equal(t, 0, result.Candidates)\n    assert.Equal(t, 0, result.Deleted)\n    assert.Equal(t, 1, result.Errors)\n}\n\nfunc TestGCCollector_Delete_StoreError(t *testing.T) {\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n    scheme.AddKnownTypes(schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"agents.x-k8s.io\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}, \n        &unstructured.Unstructured{},\n        &unstructured.UnstructuredList{},\n    )\n    \n    fakeClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClientWithCustomListKinds(scheme, map[schema.GroupVersionResource]string{\n        SandboxGVR: \"SandboxList\",\n    })\n\n    sessionID := \"test-session\"\n    \n    mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, sessionID).Return(fmt.Errorf(\"store delete error\"))\n\n    sandbox := buildTestSandbox(\"test-sandbox\", \"default\", sessionID, 10*time.Minute)\n    fakeClient.Resource(SandboxGVR).Namespace(\"default\").Create(context.Background(), sandbox, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n\n    config := DefaultGCConfig()\n    policy, _ := NewGCPolicy(config)\n    metrics := NewGCMetrics()\n\n    collector := NewGCCollector(fakeClient, mockStore, config, policy, metrics)\n\n    ctx := context.Background()\n    err := collector.Delete(ctx, sandbox, wmTypes.CleanupReasonExpired)\n\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    mockStore.AssertExpectations(t)\n}\n```\n\n**Step 3: Run tests**\n\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/gc/ -v -run TestGCCollector\n```\n\nExpected: All tests PASS\n\n**Step 4: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add pkg/workloadmanager/gc/collector_test.go\ngit commit -m \"test(ar-038): enhance gc/collector test coverage\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 2: 更新 gc/scheduler_test.go\n\n**Files:**\n- Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/scheduler_test.go`\n- Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/scheduler.go`\n\n**Step 1: Review existing tests and add missing cases**\n\n```go\n// pkg/workloadmanager/gc/scheduler_test.go\n\nfunc TestGCScheduler_Stop(t *testing.T) {\n    config := DefaultGCConfig()\n    policy, _ := NewGCPolicy(config)\n    metrics := NewGCMetrics()\n    \n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n    scheme.AddKnownTypes(schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"agents.x-k8s.io\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}, \n        &unstructured.Unstructured{},\n        &unstructured.UnstructuredList{},\n    )\n    \n    fakeClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClientWithCustomListKinds(scheme, map[schema.GroupVersionResource]string{\n        SandboxGVR: \"SandboxList\",\n    })\n\n    collector := NewGCCollector(fakeClient, mockStore, config, policy, metrics)\n    scheduler := NewGCScheduler(collector, config)\n\n    ctx, cancel := context.WithCancel(context.Background())\n\n    done := make(chan bool)\n    go func() {\n        scheduler.Run(ctx)\n        done <- true\n    }()\n\n    cancel()\n    \n    select {\n    case <-done:\n        // Scheduler stopped successfully\n    case <-time.After(5 * time.Second):\n        t.Fatal(\"Scheduler did not stop within timeout\")\n    }\n}\n\nfunc TestGCScheduler_Run_WithInterval(t *testing.T) {\n    config := &GCConfig{\n        MaxAge:        1 * time.Hour,\n        IdleTimeout:   15 * time.Minute,\n        DryRun:        true,\n        Namespaces:    []string{},\n        LabelSelector: \"\",\n        Interval:      100 * time.Millisecond,\n    }\n    policy, _ := NewGCPolicy(config)\n    metrics := NewGCMetrics()\n    \n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n    scheme.AddKnownTypes(schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"agents.x-k8s.io\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}, \n        &unstructured.Unstructured{},\n        &unstructured.UnstructuredList{},\n    )\n    \n    fakeClient := fake.NewSimpleDynamicClientWithCustomListKinds(scheme, map[schema.GroupVersionResource]string{\n        SandboxGVR: \"SandboxList\",\n    })\n\n    collector := NewGCCollector(fakeClient, mockStore, config, policy, metrics)\n    scheduler := NewGCScheduler(collector, config)\n\n    ctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(context.Background(), 500*time.Millisecond)\n    defer cancel()\n\n    scheduler.Run(ctx)\n\n    assert.True(t, metrics.GetTotalScanned() >= 1)\n}\n```\n\n**Step 2: Run tests**\n\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/gc/ -v -run TestGCScheduler\n```\n\nExpected: All tests PASS\n\n**Step 3: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add pkg/workloadmanager/gc/scheduler_test.go\ngit commit -m \"test(ar-038): enhance gc/scheduler test coverage\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 3: 更新 gc/policy_test.go\n\n**Files:**\n- Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/policy_test.go`\n- Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/policy.go`\n\n**Step 1: Review existing tests and add edge cases**\n\n```go\n// pkg/workloadmanager/gc/policy_test.go\n\nfunc TestGCPolicy_ShouldGC_ZeroAge(t *testing.T) {\n    config := &GCConfig{\n        MaxAge:        1 * time.Hour,\n        IdleTimeout:   15 * time.Minute,\n        DryRun:        false,\n        Namespaces:    []string{},\n        LabelSelector: \"\",\n    }\n    policy, _ := NewGCPolicy(config)\n\n    sandbox := &unstructured.Unstructured{\n        Object: map[string]interface{}{\n            \"apiVersion\": \"agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1\",\n            \"kind\":       \"Sandbox\",\n            \"metadata\": map[string]interface{}{\n                \"name\":      \"test-sandbox\",\n                \"namespace\": \"default\",\n                \"creationTimestamp\": time.Now().Format(time.RFC3339),\n            },\n        },\n    }\n\n    sessionInfo := &SessionInfo{\n        SessionID:        \"test-session\",\n        LastActivityAt:   time.Now(),\n        ExpiresAt:        time.Now().Add(1 * time.Hour),\n        HasActiveSession: true,\n    }\n\n    result := policy.ShouldGC(sandbox, sessionInfo)\n    assert.False(t, result)\n}\n\nfunc TestGCPolicy_ShouldGC_NamespaceFilter(t *testing.T) {\n    config := &GCConfig{\n        MaxAge:        1 * time.Hour,\n        IdleTimeout:   15 * time.Minute,\n        DryRun:        false,\n        Namespaces:    []string{\"production\"},\n        LabelSelector: \"\",\n    }\n    policy, _ := NewGCPolicy(config)\n\n    // Test with matching namespace\n    sandbox := &unstructured.Unstructured{\n        Object: map[string]interface{}{\n            \"apiVersion\": \"agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1\",\n            \"kind\":       \"Sandbox\",\n            \"metadata\": map[string]interface{}{\n                \"name\":      \"test-sandbox\",\n                \"namespace\": \"production\",\n                \"creationTimestamp\": time.Now().Add(-2 * time.Hour).Format(time.RFC3339),\n            },\n        },\n    }\n\n    sessionInfo := &SessionInfo{\n        SessionID:        \"test-session\",\n        LastActivityAt:   time.Now(),\n        ExpiresAt:        time.Now().Add(1 * time.Hour),\n        HasActiveSession: true,\n    }\n\n    result := policy.ShouldGC(sandbox, sessionInfo)\n    assert.True(t, result)\n\n    // Test with non-matching namespace\n    sandbox.SetNamespace(\"development\")\n    result = policy.ShouldGC(sandbox, sessionInfo)\n    assert.False(t, result)\n}\n\nfunc TestGCPolicy_ShouldGC_LabelSelector(t *testing.T) {\n    config := &GCConfig{\n        MaxAge:        1 * time.Hour,\n        IdleTimeout:   15 * time.Minute,\n        DryRun:        false,\n        Namespaces:    []string{},\n        LabelSelector: \"environment=test\",\n    }\n    policy, _ := NewGCPolicy(config)\n\n    // Test with matching labels\n    sandbox := &unstructured.Unstructured{\n        Object: map[string]interface{}{\n            \"apiVersion\": \"agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1\",\n            \"kind\":       \"Sandbox\",\n            \"metadata\": map[string]interface{}{\n                \"name\":      \"test-sandbox\",\n                \"namespace\": \"default\",\n                \"creationTimestamp\": time.Now().Add(-2 * time.Hour).Format(time.RFC3339),\n                \"labels\": map[string]interface{}{\n                    \"environment\": \"test\",\n                },\n            },\n        },\n    }\n\n    sessionInfo := &SessionInfo{\n        SessionID:        \"test-session\",\n        LastActivityAt:   time.Now(),\n        ExpiresAt:        time.Now().Add(1 * time.Hour),\n        HasActiveSession: true,\n    }\n\n    result := policy.ShouldGC(sandbox, sessionInfo)\n    assert.True(t, result)\n\n    // Test with non-matching labels\n    sandbox.SetLabels(map[string]interface{}{\"environment\": \"production\"})\n    result = policy.ShouldGC(sandbox, sessionInfo)\n    assert.False(t, result)\n}\n```\n\n**Step 2: Run tests**\n\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/gc/ -v -run TestGCPolicy\n```\n\nExpected: All tests PASS\n\n**Step 3: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add pkg/workloadmanager/gc/policy_test.go\ngit commit -m \"test(ar-038): enhance gc/policy test coverage\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 4: 更新 gc/metrics_test.go\n\n**Files:**\n- Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/metrics_test.go`\n- Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/gc/metrics.go`\n\n**Step 1: Review and add comprehensive metrics tests**\n\n```go\n// pkg/workloadmanager/gc/metrics_test.go\n\nfunc TestGCMetrics_Concurrent(t *testing.T) {\n    metrics := NewGCMetrics()\n\n    var wg sync.WaitGroup\n    for i := 0; i < 100; i++ {\n        wg.Add(1)\n        go func() {\n            defer wg.Done()\n            metrics.RecordScanned(1)\n            metrics.RecordDeleted(\"test\", \"Sandbox\")\n            metrics.RecordError(\"test_error\")\n        }()\n    }\n    wg.Wait()\n\n    assert.Equal(t, int64(100), metrics.GetTotalScanned())\n    assert.Equal(t, int64(100), metrics.GetTotalDeleted())\n}\n\nfunc TestGCMetrics_ResetCandidates(t *testing.T) {\n    metrics := NewGCMetrics()\n    metrics.SetCandidates(10)\n    metrics.RecordScanned(10)\n\n    metrics.ResetCandidates()\n\n    assert.Equal(t, 0, metrics.GetCandidates())\n    assert.Equal(t, int64(10), metrics.GetTotalScanned())\n}\n\nfunc TestGCMetrics_GetErrorCounts(t *testing.T) {\n    metrics := NewGCMetrics()\n    metrics.RecordError(\"find_candidates\")\n    metrics.RecordError(\"find_candidates\")\n    metrics.RecordError(\"delete\")\n    metrics.RecordError(\"find_candidates\")\n    metrics.RecordError(\"get_session_info\")\n\n    errorCounts := metrics.GetErrorCounts()\n\n    assert.Equal(t, int64(3), errorCounts[\"find_candidates\"])\n    assert.Equal(t, int64(1), errorCounts[\"delete\"])\n    assert.Equal(t, int64(1), errorCounts[\"get_session_info\"])\n}\n```\n\n**Step 2: Run tests**\n\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/gc/ -v -run TestGCMetrics\n```\n\nExpected: All tests PASS\n\n**Step 3: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add pkg/workloadmanager/gc/metrics_test.go\ngit commit -m \"test(ar-038): enhance gc/metrics test coverage\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 5: 更新 controller/sandbox_test.go（验证 TestCase-WM-001, WM-002, WM-003）\n\n**Files:**\n- Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/sandbox_test.go`\n- Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/controller/sandbox.go`\n\n**Step 1: Add comprehensive controller tests**\n\n```go\n// pkg/workloadmanager/controller/sandbox_test.go\n\n// TestCase-WM-001: 验证 Sandbox 创建接口\nfunc TestSandboxController_CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox_Success(t *testing.T) {\n    mockK8sClient := &mockK8sClient{}\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    controller := NewSandboxController(mockK8sClient, mockStore)\n\n    agentRuntime := &unstructured.Unstructured{\n        Object: map[string]interface{}{\n            \"apiVersion\": \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\",\n            \"kind\":       \"AgentRuntime\",\n            \"metadata\": map[string]interface{}{\n                \"name\":      \"test-agent\",\n                \"namespace\": \"default\",\n            },\n            \"spec\": map[string]interface{}{\n                \"podTemplate\": map[string]interface{}{\n                    \"containers\": []interface{}{\n                        map[string]interface{}{\n                            \"name\":  \"agent\",\n                            \"image\": \"test-image\",\n                        },\n                    },\n                },\n                \"ports\": []interface{}{\n                    map[string]interface{}{\n                        \"port\":     int64(8080),\n                        \"protocol\": \"HTTP\",\n                    },\n                },\n            },\n        },\n    }\n\n    mockK8sClient.On(\"GetAgentRuntime\", mock.Anything, \"default\", \"test-agent\").Return(agentRuntime, nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"StoreSandbox\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, mock.Anything).Return(nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"UpdateSandbox\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, mock.Anything).Return(nil)\n    \n    createdSandbox := &unstructured.Unstructured{\n        Object: map[string]interface{}{\n            \"metadata\": map[string]interface{}{\n                \"uid\": \"test-uid-123\",\n            },\n        },\n    }\n    mockK8sClient.On(\"CreateSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"default\", mock.Anything).Return(createdSandbox, nil)\n    mockK8sClient.On(\"GetPodIP\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, \"default\", mock.Anything).Return(\"10.0.0.1\", nil)\n\n    req := &api.CreateSandboxRequest{\n        Name:      \"test-agent\",\n        Namespace: \"default\",\n    }\n\n    resp, err := controller.CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox(context.Background(), req)\n\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.NotEmpty(t, resp.SessionID)\n    assert.NotEmpty(t, resp.SandboxID)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"10.0.0.1:8080\", resp.EntryPoints[0].Endpoint)\n    assert.NotEmpty(t, resp.CreatedAt)\n    assert.NotEmpty(t, resp.ExpiresAt)\n\n    mockK8sClient.AssertExpectations(t)\n    mockStore.AssertExpectations(t)\n}\n\n// TestCase-WM-003: 验证非法输入拦截\nfunc TestSandboxController_CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox_InvalidInput_NoPodTemplate(t *testing.T) {\n    mockK8sClient := &mockK8sClient{}\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    controller := NewSandboxController(mockK8sClient, mockStore)\n\n    agentRuntime := &unstructured.Unstructured{\n        Object: map[string]interface{}{\n            \"apiVersion\": \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\",\n            \"kind\":       \"AgentRuntime\",\n            \"metadata\": map[string]interface{}{\n                \"name\":      \"test-agent\",\n                \"namespace\": \"default\",\n            },\n            \"spec\": map[string]interface{}{},\n        },\n    }\n\n    mockK8sClient.On(\"GetAgentRuntime\", mock.Anything, \"default\", \"test-agent\").Return(agentRuntime, nil)\n\n    req := &api.CreateSandboxRequest{\n        Name:      \"test-agent\",\n        Namespace: \"default\",\n    }\n\n    resp, err := controller.CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox(context.Background(), req)\n\n    assert.Error(t, err)\n    assert.Nil(t, resp)\n    assert.Contains(t, err.Error(), \"failed to get ports\")\n\n    mockK8sClient.AssertExpectations(t)\n}\n\n// TestCase-WM-003: 验证 AgentRuntime 不存在\nfunc TestSandboxController_CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox_NotFound(t *testing.T) {\n    mockK8sClient := &mockK8sClient{}\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    controller := NewSandboxController(mockK8sClient, mockStore)\n\n    notFoundErr := apierrors.NewNotFound(schema.GroupResource{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Resource: \"agentruntimes\"}, \"test-agent\")\n    mockK8sClient.On(\"GetAgentRuntime\", mock.Anything, \"default\", \"test-agent\").Return(nil, notFoundErr)\n\n    req := &api.CreateSandboxRequest{\n        Name:      \"test-agent\",\n        Namespace: \"default\",\n    }\n\n    resp, err := controller.CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox(context.Background(), req)\n\n    assert.Error(t, err)\n    assert.Nil(t, resp)\n    assert.Contains(t, err.Error(), \"not found\")\n\n    mockK8sClient.AssertExpectations(t)\n}\n\nfunc TestSandboxController_GetSession_Success(t *testing.T) {\n    mockK8sClient := &mockK8sClient{}\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    controller := NewSandboxController(mockK8sClient, mockStore)\n\n    sandboxInfo := &types.SandboxInfo{\n        SessionID:    \"test-session\",\n        SandboxID:    \"sandbox-123\",\n        SandboxName:  \"test-sandbox\",\n        WorkloadName: \"test-agent\",\n        Namespace:    \"default\",\n        Kind:         \"AgentRuntime\",\n        Status:       \"running\",\n        CreatedAt:    time.Now(),\n        ExpiresAt:    time.Now().Add(8 * time.Hour),\n        LastActivityAt: time.Now(),\n        PodIP:        \"10.0.0.1\",\n        EntryPoints: []types.SandboxEntryPoint{\n            {\n                Protocol: \"HTTP\",\n                Endpoint: \"10.0.0.1:8080\",\n            },\n        },\n    }\n\n    mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"test-session\").Return(sandboxInfo, nil)\n\n    resp, err := controller.GetSession(context.Background(), \"test-session\")\n\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"test-session\", resp.SessionID)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"sandbox-123\", resp.SandboxID)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"test-sandbox\", resp.SandboxName)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"AgentRuntime\", resp.Kind)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"10.0.0.1\", resp.PodIP)\n    assert.Len(t, resp.EntryPoints, 1)\n\n    mockStore.AssertExpectations(t)\n}\n\nfunc TestSandboxController_GetSession_NotFound(t *testing.T) {\n    mockK8sClient := &mockK8sClient{}\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    controller := NewSandboxController(mockK8sClient, mockStore)\n\n    mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"non-existent\").Return(nil, store.ErrNotFound)\n\n    resp, err := controller.GetSession(context.Background(), \"non-existent\")\n\n    assert.Error(t, err)\n    assert.Nil(t, resp)\n    assert.Contains(t, err.Error(), \"not found\")\n\n    mockStore.AssertExpectations(t)\n}\n\nfunc TestSandboxController_DeleteSession_Success(t *testing.T) {\n    mockK8sClient := &mockK8sClient{}\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    controller := NewSandboxController(mockK8sClient, mockStore)\n\n    sandboxInfo := &types.SandboxInfo{\n        SessionID:    \"test-session\",\n        SandboxID:    \"sandbox-123\",\n        SandboxName:  \"test-sandbox\",\n        SandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n    }\n\n    mockStore.On(\"GetSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"test-session\").Return(sandboxInfo, nil)\n    mockK8sClient.On(\"DeleteSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"default\", \"test-sandbox\").Return(nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"DeleteSandboxBySessionID\", mock.Anything, \"test-session\").Return(nil)\n\n    resp, err := controller.DeleteSession(context.Background(), \"test-session\")\n\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"test-session\", resp.SessionID)\n    assert.NotEmpty(t, resp.DeletedAt)\n\n    mockK8sClient.AssertExpectations(t)\n    mockStore.AssertExpectations(t)\n}\n\nfunc TestSandboxController_CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox_Success(t *testing.T) {\n    mockK8sClient := &mockK8sClient{}\n    mockStore := &mockStore{}\n    controller := NewSandboxController(mockK8sClient, mockStore)\n\n    codeInterpreter := &unstructured.Unstructured{\n        Object: map[string]interface{}{\n            \"apiVersion\": \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\",\n            \"kind\":       \"CodeInterpreter\",\n            \"metadata\": map[string]interface{}{\n                \"name\":      \"test-code-int\",\n                \"namespace\": \"default\",\n            },\n            \"spec\": map[string]interface{}{\n                \"template\": map[string]interface{}{\n                    \"image\": \"python:3.11-slim\",\n                },\n            },\n        },\n    }\n\n    mockK8sClient.On(\"GetCodeInterpreter\", mock.Anything, \"default\", \"test-code-int\").Return(codeInterpreter, nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"StoreSandbox\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, mock.Anything).Return(nil)\n    mockStore.On(\"UpdateSandbox\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, mock.Anything).Return(nil)\n    \n    createdSandbox := &unstructured.Unstructured{\n        Object: map[string]interface{}{\n            \"metadata\": map[string]interface{}{\n                \"uid\": \"test-uid-456\",\n            },\n        },\n    }\n    mockK8sClient.On(\"CreateSandbox\", mock.Anything, \"default\", mock.Anything).Return(createdSandbox, nil)\n    mockK8sClient.On(\"GetPodIP\", mock.Anything, mock.Anything, \"default\", mock.Anything).Return(\"10.0.0.2\", nil)\n\n    req := &api.CreateSandboxRequest{\n        Name:      \"test-code-int\",\n        Namespace: \"default\",\n    }\n\n    resp, err := controller.CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox(context.Background(), req)\n\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.NotEmpty(t, resp.SessionID)\n    assert.NotEmpty(t, resp.SandboxID)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"10.0.0.2:8080\", resp.EntryPoints[0].Endpoint)\n\n    mockK8sClient.AssertExpectations(t)\n    mockStore.AssertExpectations(t)\n}\n```\n\n**Step 2: Run tests**\n\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/controller/ -v\n```\n\nExpected: All tests PASS\n\n**Step 3: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add pkg/workloadmanager/controller/sandbox_test.go\ngit commit -m \"test(ar-038): comprehensive controller tests (TestCase-WM-001, WM-002, WM-003)\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Task 6: 更新 handler/handler_test.go\n\n**Files:**\n- Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/handler_test.go`\n- Verify: `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/handler.go`\n\n**Step 1: Add handler HTTP tests**\n\n```go\n// pkg/workloadmanager/handler/handler_test.go\n\nfunc TestHandler_CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox_InvalidJSON(t *testing.T) {\n    gin.SetMode(gin.TestMode)\n    \n    mockController := &mockController{}\n    handler := NewHandler(mockController)\n\n    router := gin.New()\n    router.POST(\"/agent-runtime\", handl