{"type":"text","timestamp":1775892153513,"sessionID":"ses_28499ca24ffe6NCAYwqRAm1Cei","part":{"id":"prt_d7b6baf6a001PfCj4A8m6FKAnm","messageID":"msg_d7b6b8319001mgcHu4Ih5KRtU6","sessionID":"ses_28499ca24ffe6NCAYwqRAm1Cei","type":"text","text":"I've created a comprehensive `tasks.md` file for AR-038 (Go 单元测试 for workloadmanager). The plan breaks down the work into **19 atomic, independently verifiable tasks**:\n\n## Overview\n\n**Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n**Size:** L (Large)  \n**Goal:** Achieve >80% test coverage across all components\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### GC Package (4 tasks)\n- Task 1: Update `gc/collector_test.go` \n- Task 2: Update `gc/scheduler_test.go`\n- Task 3: Update `gc/policy_test.go`\n- Task 4: Update `gc/metrics_test.go`\n\n### Controller (2 tasks)\n- Task 5: Update `controller/sandbox_test.go` (validates TestCase-WM-001, WM-002, WM-003)\n- Task 14: Create `controller/reconciler/controller_test.go`\n\n### Handler (2 tasks)\n- Task 6: Update `handler/handler_test.go`\n- Task 7: Update `handler/sandbox_test.go`\n\n### Client, Auth, Middleware, Config, API (5 tasks)\n- Task 8: Update `client/k8s_client_test.go`\n- Task 9: Create `auth/k8s_auth_test.go`\n- Task 10: Update `middleware/middleware_test.go`\n- Task 11: Update `config/config_test.go`\n- Task 12: Update `api/response_test.go`\n\n### Garbage Collector & Types (2 tasks)\n- Task 13: Update `garbage_collector_test.go`\n- Task 15: Create `types/sandbox_types_test.go`\n\n### Verification (4 tasks)\n- Task 16: Run all tests and verify >80% coverage\n- Task 17: Run `go vet` and linting checks\n- Task 18: Verify test_spec.md requirements (TestCase-WM-001, WM-002, WM-003)\n- Task 19: Final validation and cleanup\n\nEach task follows the pattern: **Write tests → Run tests → Verify → Commit**\n\nThe plan ensures comprehensive coverage of all core components while validating the specific test cases from `test_spec.md`.","time":{"start":1775892153511,"end":1775892153511}}}
